sentences.english: At small block sizes, compression is much worse than file-level compression.
sentences.chinese: 塊大小比較小時，壓縮比文件級別壓縮差很多。

sentences.english: The compression ratios were noted from individual products' log files.
sentences.chinese: 壓縮比是從單個產品的日誌文件標記錄出來的。

sentences.english: The main focus of this group is to achieve the highest compression ratio.
sentences.chinese: 這類壓縮器主要側重於實現最高的壓縮比。

sentences.english: A very fast Free lossless audio format with good compression.
sentences.chinese: 一種免費的快速且壓縮比很好的無損音頻格式。

sentences.english: They. however, can achieve a better compression ratio.
sentences.chinese: 但是，它們可以實現更好的壓縮比。

sentences.english: Next I looked at the compression ratios.
sentences.chinese: 接下來，我研究的是壓縮比。

sentences.english: Results show highter compnaion ratio were obtained using polar-log cooulinatemappmg as preprocessor.
sentences.chinese: 結果表明以極對數映射作預處理器壓縮比高。

sentences.english: Wavelet-based compression can be much more efficient than older types.
sentences.chinese: 基於小波的壓縮比其他類型有高得多的效率。

sentences.english: The lossless mode has a low compression ratio that allows perfect reconstruction of the original image.
sentences.chinese: 無損模式壓縮比低，允許完美重現圖像。

sentences.english: Pulse shaping is the important methods to get high compression ratio.
sentences.chinese: 輻射驅動溫度源脈衝整形是獲得高壓縮比的重要途徑。
